# FleetX System Architecture

Version: 1.0

---

# 1. Architecture Overview

FleetX follows a modular layered architecture designed for maintainability, scalability, and future cloud deployment.

The system is divided into four primary layers:

- Presentation Layer
- Application Layer
- Data Layer
- External Integration Layer

---

# 2. High-Level Architecture

```text
                React Frontend
                      │
          REST API / WebSocket
                      │
              FastAPI Backend
                      │
 ┌────────────────────────────────────┐
 │ Authentication Service             │
 │ Shipment Service                   │
 │ Dispatch Service                   │
 │ Fleet Service                      │
 │ Driver Service                     │
 │ Trip Service                       │
 │ Maintenance Service                │
 │ Fuel Service                       │
 │ Analytics Service                  │
 │ Notification Service               │
 │ AI Service                         │
 └────────────────────────────────────┘
                      │
          Repository Layer
                      │
              PostgreSQL Database
                      │
     External Services (Future)
```

---

